        { "p": "el-",  "hu": "elvesz",  "en": "to take away; to lose",            "ex": [["Elveszi tőle.","He takes it from her."],["Elveszett a kulcs.","The key was lost."]] },
        { "p": "fel-", "hu": "felvesz", "en": "to pick up; to put on; to hire; to record", "ex": [["Felveszi a kabátját.","She puts on her coat."],["Felvesz alkalmazottat.","He hires an employee."]] },
